Deanacyastityktaxea

Deanacyastityktaxea is a female creature in the Creation of Marlien which is a half-breed of succubus and Charon memitim.

She is a favoured Fourth_wall-breaking and world-breaking tool of the writer, frequently referencing things from Totum or the real world despite no in-universe explanation for why she might be able to travel between creations. She also makes direct appearances before mortals on The Material Plane of Marlien and otherwise flouts the the laws of the Charon to an extent, making excuses that due to her imperfect heritage she finds it difficult to properly transpose herself to the right time or location. As a result, she is at the centre of Material Plane legends of the Blackbird.

History

Deanacyastityktaxea is the daughter of the famed Memitim Mikaotrexeaonoa and an unknown succubus.
